name: Graphic Technical Knit Mitten Top
shortDescription: This sleek colour-blocked top forms the base layer of this season’s ski capsule. An exposed zip allows the high neckline to be styled up or down, while the long sleeves extend to the knuckles and are finished with thumb holes for a built-in mitten effect.

• Main material: 42% polyester, 34% wool, 23% polyamide, 1% polyurethane
  • Milk White
  • Made in Italy
